  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CommandForTesting, DeleteStall, EditStallSave, LoginCommands, UpdateCommand

    public abstract class Commands
extends Model<ViewInterface>
    Created by Kevin L on 3/2/2016. This is part of command pattern So we can manage undo/redo as well as offline behaviour This is the super class. It contains some methods that currently does nothing, and if the child class needs to use it must override. Not all child class will use all methods, but all abstract methods must exist.
